================================================================================
PERSONAL USE — FREE (No License Required)
================================================================================

You may freely use, modify, and build from these designs for personal,
educational, and non-commercial purposes. This includes:

  - Building batteries for your own use
  - Building for friends, family, or neighbors (no charge)
  - Teaching workshops or classes (free/educational only)
  - Forking, modifying, and sharing your modifications
  - Academic research and experimentation

No attribution is required for personal use, though it is appreciated.
Link back to https://github.com/Breed2085/ChipMonkeysOffGrid if you share
your modifications.

================================================================================
COMMERCIAL USE — License Required (10% Royalty)
================================================================================

Commercial use of these designs requires a Commercial Kit-Seller License
from ChipMonkeys Inc.

"Commercial use" means any activity where money changes hands and these
designs (or derivatives of these designs) are the product or a substantial
component of the product being sold. This includes but is not limited to:

  - Selling kits, components, or assembled systems
  - Selling pre-made membranes, electrodes, or electrolyte
  - Selling modified or improved versions of these designs
  - Offering paid workshops where these designs are the primary content
  - Including these designs in a product sold by a third party

LICENSE TERMS:

  1. REGISTRATION: Apply at https://monkeybusinessmanager.com/offgrid/license
     Registration is free. All applications are reviewed by ChipMonkeys Inc.

  2. ROYALTY: 10% of gross revenue from all products that incorporate or are
     based on ChipMonkeys Off Grid designs. Revenue means total sales, not
     profit. Royalties are due quarterly.

  3. DOCUMENTATION: Licensees must maintain a log of all orders (date,
     customer, amount) and make this log available to ChipMonkeys Inc.
     upon request.

  4. ATTRIBUTION: Products and product listings must include the statement:
     "Based on ChipMonkeys Off Grid designs — chipmonkeysinc.com/offgrid"

  5. ROYALTY PURPOSE: All royalties collected are directed toward the
     furtherment of the ChipMonkeys Off Grid project — R&D, documentation,
     tooling, and community development.

