ENFORCEMENT
================================================================================

This is an honor system. We trust the community. But the designs in this
repository are copyrighted works of ChipMonkeys Inc. and this license is
legally binding.

If you are found to be profiting from these designs without a commercial
license and without paying the required royalties:

  - ChipMonkeys Inc. will pursue legal action to the fullest extent of
    the law.
  - This includes recovery of ALL profits derived from unauthorized use,
    statutory damages, and attorney's fees.
  - We will seek injunctive relief to stop unauthorized sales immediately.

Don't test us on this. Just sign up, pay the 10%, and build something great.
The royalty funds the project that makes your business possible.

